message.body: Saw you at the light at Landover and Haverford. Beer run.
Haha nice. I was coming from or going to my dads with Jack. It's a bachelor pad here tonight. Gillian is at a bachelorette party in DC for the night.
Hey, would you be available to come by sometime and give us some advice on our deck?

I started removing some of the boards which are in the worst shape and replacing them. Problem is, the replacement boards I got are pine and I am pretty certain the deck is some sort of cedar, but I don't know which sort. I also don't know if I need to re
Sure I can come by tomorrow
Awesome, thanks! Anytime that works for you works for us.
Hey, running to Home Depot. What's your schedule like today?
Just getting jack to sleep for his morning nap. After that I'm free till his afternoon nap then a lax game at 4
I was thinking of walking over after he eats
Cool. I'll let you know when we're back.
Cool. Jack is still asleep ill let you know when we are heading over. We will probably walk over.
